Weblogs and learning
Two papers written by Christian Wagner and others:

<a href="http://wagnernet.com/tiki/tiki-download_file.php?fileId=7">Supporting Knowledge Management in Organizations with Conversational Technologies: Discussion Forums,  Weblogs, and Wikis (pdf)</a>. It is a review of these technologies for learning applications.

To appear in JOURNAL OF DATABASE MANAGEMENT, 16 (2): I-VIII APR-JUN 2005.

The other one is <a href="http://wagnernet.com/tiki/tiki-download_file.php?fileId=8">Learning with weblogs: An Empirical Investigation (pdf)</a>.

In Proceedings, HICSS-38, January 2005. 

